## ğŸ” Data Pipeline Zones

This project follows a **Landing â†’ Trusted â†’ Curated** architecture:

### 1. **Landing Zone**

Raw data is registered in the Glue Data Catalog using Athena DDL scripts.

*Example scripts:*
- [`customer_landing.sql`](./screenshots/Athena%20SQL/customer_landing.sql)
- [`accelerometer_landing.sql`](./screenshots/Athena%20SQL/accelerometer_landing.sql)
- [`step_trainer_landing.sql`](./screenshots/Athena%20SQL/step_trainer_landing.sql)

